HEADWORD: Hyacinthine
<hw>Hy`a*cin"thine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>hyacinthinus</ets>, Gr. <?/.]</ety> <def>Belonging to the hyacinth;
